      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为技能注册表（Skill Registry）设计一个状态流转图。这个系统对接HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault，数据从保险库出来后先进入idle状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault",
        "idle"
