      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，idle是初始状态。那用户触发SCAN操作后会到哪里？是直接进入viewing查看详情，还是先有个中间状态？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "idle",
        "SCAN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "先进入scanned状态，表示已扫描但未查看详情。从scanned可以SELECT进入viewing状态，也可以继续SCAN更新列表。另外scanned和viewing都要支持EXPORT操作。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "scanned",
        "viewing",
        "SELECT",
        "EXPORT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把主干画出来：idle通过SCAN到scanned，scanned通过SELECT到viewing。两个状态都加上自循环的EXPORT。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "idle",
        "scanned",
        "viewing",
        "SCAN",
        "SELECT",
        "EXPORT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，scanned还要能自循环SCAN，因为可以多次扫描更新。viewing里也可以SELECT切换不同条目。另外需要BACK返回scanned，以及RESET回到idle。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "scanned",
        "viewing",
        "SCAN",
        "SELECT",
        "BACK",
        "RESET"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "加上了scanned的自循环SCAN、viewing的自循环SELECT，还有BACK和RESET。检查下：scanned到idle是RESET，viewing到scanned是BACK。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "scanned",
        "viewing",
        "idle",
        "RESET",
        "BACK"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，viewing的自循环SELECT我确认一下——在查看状态下切换条目，应该还是停留在viewing，这个是对的。但scanned的EXPORT自循环你画了吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "scanned",
