      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "有的，scanned和viewing都有EXPORT自循环。最终结构：从HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault进入idle，SCAN到scanned，SELECT进viewing，BACK返回，RESET回idle，两个状态都能反复EXPORT。",
